NAME
    PPIx::LineToSub - Find the package and subroutine by line

SYNOPSIS
      use PPIx::LineToSub;
      my $document = PPI::Document->new('t/hello.pl');
      $document->index_line_to_sub;

      my($package, $sub) = $document->line_to_sub(1);

DESCRIPTION
    PPIx::LineToSub is a module which, given a Perl file and a line number,
    will return the package and sub in effect.

SEE ALSO
    PPI.

